Để anh mang lên giúp em.

00:25:41.320 --> 00:25:42.040
Đóng cốp giúp anh.

00:25:42.200 --> 00:25:42.720
Ừ.

00:25:43.920 --> 00:25:44.440
Cảm ơn.

00:25:45.920 --> 00:25:46.400
Đi thôi.

00:25:57.840 --> 00:25:58.480
Chờ chút.

